dash|ON|FF_DOF E200,1000|FF_DOF E201,1000|FF_DOF E625,1000|FF_DOF E629,1000|FF_PC,U,E,animation/overlay/mameoutput/generic_explosion-blue|FF_PC,U,D,ledstrip/batch?zones=right_matrix~matrix_8x8_explosion3~LED_R!~!LED_G!~!LED_B!~250~1~false@left_matrix~matrix_8x8_explosion3~LED_R!~!LED_G!~!LED_B!~250~1~false
coin|ON|FF_DOF E78,0
player1|ON|FF_DOF E78,0
player2|ON|FF_DOF E78,0

